    "• 'Lump' or 'mass' with no indication of cancer (e.g.",
    "breast lump) are labelled 'no malignancy'.",
    "• Where resected year is redacted and 'no recurrence' is mentioned, the text is deemed 'no malignancy'.",
    "• Grade one meningioma is 'no malignancy'.",
    "Benign menigioma would also be 'no malignancy', but if only 'meningioma' is mentioned, this would be 'possible malignancy (ambiguous)'."
